            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "祂在何处？"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "转过身来，看见复活耶稣；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "以为是园丁，我竟未认出；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "以为他知主在何处。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "祂在何处？"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "何处寻祂─主耶稣？"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "何处寻祂─爱主？"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "何处寻祂─指示我路，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我要取祂，不畏险阻。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我听见祂对我柔声轻诉；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "甜美呼唤进入我心深处。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "熟悉声音，就是我主；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "是我耶稣！"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我已寻见主耶稣，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我已寻见爱主，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我已寻见我心所慕，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "耶稣，挚爱，我爱你，主。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "得见我主，我心喜难述；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "祂要升天，使父心满意足。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "祂神、祂父成我们神、"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我们的父。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "你要升天，去见父；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "要我告诉门徒："
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "你神已成我们的神，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "你父已成我们的父。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
